rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Waking up to a morning with Shin's
cooking... it's the absolute best.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0004
rows.name: You ate that up in no time.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0006
rows.name: Was that not enough for you?

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0009
rows.name:
You don't have to be afraid.
I know he looks like that,
but Shin's not angry.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0011
rows.name:
He's just worried about you,
Satahiko. Worried you didn't
get enough to eat.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0014
rows.name:
I know Shin seems scary,
but he's actually really kind.
You'll get used to him.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0016
rows.name:
I'm going to clean up.
We'll head out as soon
as I'm finished.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0017
rows.name:
Right. We're almost at Felt Village,
and we can meet up with Kasumi.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0018
rows.name:
Yeah. It's still a ways,
but it's a straight shot from here.
We won't get lost.
